<!ELEMENT Attribute                 (#PCDATA)>
<!-- can be one of the following; see LinkOut SubjectTypes and Attributes 
 at http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/linkout/doc/subjecttypes.html for a description 
 of these elements:
//BARRIERS
